<note n="0431001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431001">常＝來【聖】【甲】</note>
<note n="0431002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431002">以＝似【聖】</note>
<note n="0431003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431003">或＝惑【聖】</note>
<note n="0431004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431004">雖＝難【甲】</note>
<note n="0431005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431005">復＝<g ref="#CB13663">󳕟</g>【聖】</note>
<note n="0431006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431006">智＝知【聖】【甲】</note>
<note n="0432001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0432001">此下甲本奧書曰觀應元年庚寅十一月七日於大和州大御輪寺點寫之畢為西大寺每年講經御本而已願以點寫力上生都率天願共諸眾生奉見彌勒佛大御輪寺金剛資圓宗生年六十五夏次四十五</note>
</p>
